title: Can't get fixed dialing numbers to work. I have my pin2, asks to reset, won't take reset code
content: trying to turn on fixed number dialing in call settings.  Need a pin2 code which i was able to get from tmobile.  When enter oin2 code asks to reset to a new code.  doesn't take new code.  treats entering a new code as a failed attempt.
category: Contacts, Calls, Voicemail, Google Pixel 3a XL
